{"tid":1823243,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"「緊急」有手足夜晚晚，扎醒左瞓唔番","createTime":"2020-01-13T13:45:14.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-14T03:18:18.000Z","uid":341589,"like":5,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"abcf09a500f7c294417d907357f1e3c15e79bca9","tid":1823243,"uid":341589,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-13T13:45:14.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: green;\">唔好意思！標題與內文不附</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">致各位和理非、不論您係淺黃、廢中、廢老：<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">「訓醒左，唔好繼續扮訓」</span></span>。<br />\n<br />\n請睇清楚呢排港共同班黑狗做緊咩？ 不斷冷處理示威遊行，不斷大圍捕，呢幾日搵班建制廢老9up 721 係某某民主派策劃，試圖漂白黑警。到今日油塘單嘢，拍哂片都可以話無可疑........當我地香港人白癡低能。<br />\n<br />\n其實<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">港共好清楚，香港人係適應力極強，亦<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">好善忘</span></span></strong></span></span>，所以只要每日陰D陰D，唔覺唔覺，又會好似以前咁，可以溫水煮蛙。所以唔該各位訓醒左，就做D有意義嘅事。明白好多和理非覺得自己未必有能力去改變好多事，但至少您可以去關心一下身邊發生嘅事，<span style=\"color: green;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>得閒幫下口</strong></span></span>。舉例，有人話721係班民主派帶人入去，咁班黑警當時點解唔制止，仲要關閉警署？記住同參加遊行一樣，多您一個好多。<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">今天開始多聽、多講、唔好縱容身邊一些歪理存在。</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: green;\">母忘初心，五大訴求，缺一不可。</span></span></span>"},{"pid":"af4128f8fda21887c05458736410e4dca2b82ad2","tid":1823243,"uid":341589,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-13T13:45:47.000Z","msg":"P 牌推唔到"},{"pid":"7673eefa8ae5a43c75143052a354ec52465df056","tid":1823243,"uid":341589,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-13T13:47:21.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">幫幫手，身邊好多<strong><span style=\"color: green;\">淺黃</span></strong>，剛醒左又訓返。真係提少兩日，以為無事發生。</span></span>"},{"pid":"d6a4fdd5dd822d861b5a570cac7f77cd0db08f09","tid":1823243,"uid":341589,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-13T13:47:43.000Z","msg":"<strong><em><span style=\"font-size: large;\">推俾多D人睇</span></em></strong>"},{"pid":"5ad15d46b22e870cd703d38c33550508fd9d6349","tid":1823243,"uid":341589,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-13T13:51:30.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"8163e94b6e8df68dfdc9bd368bfde3deff59de1c","tid":1823243,"uid":341589,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-13T13:52:12.000Z","msg":"P 牌推唔到"},{"pid":"8a3e95710220a7a94d60d1652003fbdd9102effc","tid":1823243,"uid":341589,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-13T13:52:42.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong><em>醒左唔好訓</em></strong></span>"},{"pid":"2f2eec6119a2eaf590aba39dd1f86b473baba597","tid":1823243,"uid":341589,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"8a3e95710220a7a94d60d1652003fbdd9102effc","tid":1823243,"uid":341589,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-13T13:52:42.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong><em>醒左唔好訓</em></strong></span>"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-13T13:53:08.000Z","msg":"<strong><em>醒左唔好訓</em></strong>"},{"pid":"3cd702b14a3d70b4f6aeb7a01bf341046ba61bdf","tid":1823243,"uid":341589,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"2f2eec6119a2eaf590aba39dd1f86b473baba597","tid":1823243,"uid":341589,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"8a3e95710220a7a94d60d1652003fbdd9102effc","tid":1823243,"uid":341589,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-13T13:52:42.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong><em>醒左唔好訓</em></strong></span>"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-13T13:53:08.000Z","msg":"<strong><em>醒左唔好訓</em></strong>"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-13T13:53:21.000Z","msg":"<strong><em>醒左唔好訓</em></strong>"},{"pid":"8ba643d7ebded49bb1668022d447db1c7e3d3346","tid":1823243,"uid":341589,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"p